# Square Root of the Golden Ratio

> Square root of the [Golden ratio][phi] (Ï†).

<section class="usage">

## Usage

``` javascript
var SQRT_PHI = require( '@stdlib/math/constants/float64-sqrt-phi' );
```

#### SQRT_PHI

Square root of the [golden ratio][phi].

``` javascript
SQRT_PHI === 1.272019649514069;
```

<!-- </usage> -->
